original_title: Tonic Sol-fa: If I Can Dream
overview: Live concert footage and behind the scenes shots and interviews make up this captivating video, of the contemporary acappella group, Tonic Sol-fa. Filmed primarily on their 2008 Tour at Hoyt Sherman Place Theater in Des Moines, Iowa, you'll get an opportunity to join in the energy and vocal performance of Greg, Jared, Mark and Shaun, that is Tonic Sol-fa. Included, are a few additional extras, that will be appreciated by new and old fans alike.
title: Tonic Sol-fa: If I Can Dream
